617
01:18:56,460 --> 01:19:00,499
Grandma, please!
Stop it, I beg you.

618
01:19:00,500 --> 01:19:05,062
Ibrahim, my dear son.

619
01:19:17,620 --> 01:19:19,975
Stop it.
Let's go, please.

620
01:19:31,020 --> 01:19:31,862
Ibrahim.

621
01:19:33,020 --> 01:19:34,658
